'''尼樂·勒梅'''（{{lang-en|Nicolas Flamel}}）是[[J·K·羅琳|J·K·羅琳]]所著[[奇幻小說|奇幻小說]]《[[哈利波特|哈利波特]]》系列中的虛構人物，原型是真實歷史上的[[尼古拉·弗拉梅爾|同名人物]]。小說裡他是唯一一位能夠製造[[賢者之石|魔法石]]的人<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://www.britishlibrary.cn/zh-hk/articles/harry-potter-a-brief-history-of-magic/|title=哈利波特：魔法簡史|author=朱利安·哈里森|work=大英圖書館|accessdate=2018-10-07|language=zh-HK|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180106160000/http://www.britishlibrary.cn/zh-hk/articles/harry-potter-a-brief-history-of-magic/|archive-date=2018-01-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因而與妻子能夠長生不老。他與[[霍格華茲|霍格華茲]]校長[[鄧不利多|鄧不利多]]也是多年的老友<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=https://star.ettoday.net/news/1043816|title=哈利波特魔法石秘密公開！神秘巫師現身《怪獸與牠們2》|author=許瑞麟|date=2017-11-02|newspaper=ETtoday星光雲|accessdate=2018-10-07|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2018-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007145616/https://star.ettoday.net/news/1043816|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《{{哈利波特1}}》的時候，已有665歲的尼樂·勒梅與妻子於[[德文郡|德文郡]]過著平靜的生活<ref name=":0" />，他將魔法石交給鄧不利多代為保管。同時，[[佛地魔|佛地魔]]為了重生而派遣[[奎若|奎若]]教授奪取魔法石，但遭[[哈利·波特_(角色)|哈利]]、[[榮恩·衛斯理|榮恩]]與[[妙麗·格蘭傑|妙麗]]阻止。為避免魔法石落入壞人之手，尼樂·勒梅與鄧不利多一致認為魔法石必須被摧毀，他存放了足夠的長生不老藥讓夫妻兩人能夠將後事安排妥當；魔法石被摧毀一段時間後，尼樂·勒梅夫妻也死去。<ref>{{Cite book|title=哈利波特——神秘的魔法石|last=J·K·羅琳|publisher=皇冠文化|year=2001年3月|isbn=957-33-1724-9|location=臺北}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.jkrowling.com/textonly/en/rumours_view.cfm?id=32|title=Section: Rumours -Nicolas Flamel is going to come to Hogwarts to teach potions|accessdate=2018-10-07|author=J.K.Rowling|publisher=J.K.Rowling Official Site|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110623030719/http://www.jkrowling.com/textonly/en/rumours_view.cfm?id=32|archivedate=2011-06-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

羅琳在[[Pottermore|Pottermore]]網站上透露了有關尼樂·勒梅的背景訊息，他出身於[[法國|法國]]的魔法學校[[波巴洞|波巴洞]]學院<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2018/07/26/nicolas-flamel-explained-who-is-the-harry-potter-and-fantastic-beasts-character|title=Nicolas Flamel Explained: Who Is the Ancient Harry Potter and Fantastic Beasts Character?|accessdate=2018-10-07|date=2018-07-26|last=Schedeen|first=Jesse|work=IGN|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007145616/https://www.ign.com/articles/2018/07/26/nicolas-flamel-explained-who-is-the-harry-potter-and-fantastic-beasts-character|archive-date=2018-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/childrens-books-site/2016/mar/08/magic-schools-around-the-world-guide-jk-rowling-harry-potter|title=Magic schools in JK Rowling's wizarding world - what you need to know|accessdate=2018-10-19|author=|date=2016-03-08|last=Golding|first=Lily|publisher=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2018-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181019205654/https://www.theguardian.com/childrens-books-site/2016/mar/08/magic-schools-around-the-world-guide-jk-rowling-harry-potter|dead-url=no}}</ref>。勒梅在致富後資助了波巴洞學院，波巴洞中的[[噴泉|噴泉]]即是以尼樂·勒梅夫妻命名的<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.storm.mg/lifestyle/607901|title=麻瓜必讀！看《怪獸與葛林戴華德的罪行》前該知道的5件事，原來鄧不利多有段心碎同志戀情|author=黃瑜敏|date=2018-11-12|work=風傳媒|accessdate=2018-11-13|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2018-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181112220215/https://www.storm.mg/lifestyle/607901|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==原型==
尼樂·勒梅的原型即為歷史上[[14世紀|14世紀]]的法國煉金術士[[尼古拉·弗拉梅爾|尼古拉·弗拉梅爾]]<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2002/nov/08/artsfeatures.harrypotter|title=World wide wizard|accessdate=2018-10-07|date=2002-11-08|last=Gittings|first=John|publisher=the Guardian|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012172016/http://www.theguardian.com/culture/2002/nov/08/artsfeatures.harrypotter|archive-date=2015-10-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。羅琳表示她在撰寫《神秘的魔法石》期間曾夢到尼樂·勒梅的[[實驗室|實驗室]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pottermore.com/writing-by-jk-rowling/nicolas-flamel|title=Nicolas Flamel|accessdate=2018-10-07|author=J.K. Rowling|publisher=Pottermore|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171112021519/https://www.pottermore.com/writing-by-jk-rowling/nicolas-flamel|archive-date=2017-11-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20180329/57151348_0.shtml|title=哈利·波特考据学：书中的很多东西，在历史上都确有其事|accessdate=2018-10-19|date=2018-03-29|publisher=鳳凰網|archive-date=2018-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181019205702/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20180329/57151348_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==電影==
在電影版《[[哈利波特：神秘的魔法石_(電影)|哈利波特：神秘的魔法石]]》中尼樂·勒梅並未出現<ref name=":2" />。

不過，後來尼樂·勒梅於哈利波特前傳「[[怪獸系列電影|怪獸系列電影]]」的第二部《[[怪獸與葛林戴華德的罪行|怪獸與葛林戴華德的罪行]]》登場，由[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]演員{{le|布朗提斯·尤杜洛斯基|Brontis Jodorowsky}}飾演<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.tvbs.com.tw/entertainment/959844|title=《怪獸2》神秘角色現身　連結《哈利波特1》|accessdate=2018-10-07|author=沈瑾暘|date=2018-07-22|publisher=TVBS新聞網|archive-date=2018-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181008121949/https://news.tvbs.com.tw/entertainment/959844|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.worldscreen.com.tw/goods.php?goods_id=15807|title=【哈利波特】傳奇魔法師加入！【怪獸與牠們的產地2】全新劇照曝光|accessdate=2018-10-07|date=2017-10-23|publisher=世界電影雜誌|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180407173537/http://www.worldscreen.com.tw/goods.php?goods_id=15807|archive-date=2018-04-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/2017-11-02/doc-ifynnnsc3680515.shtml|title=哈利波特魔法石秘密公开 神秘巫师现身《动物2》|accessdate=2018-10-07|date=2017-11-02|publisher=新浪娱乐|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171102070826/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/2017-11-02/doc-ifynnnsc3680515.shtml|archive-date=2017-11-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dailystar.co.uk/movies/718111/fantastic-beats-crimes-grindelwald-nicholas-flamel-dumbledore-newt-scamander-harry-potter|title=Fantastic Beasts: Crimes of Grindelwald sees a VERY familiar character return|date=2018-07-22|newspaper=Dailystar.co.uk|accessdate=2018-10-07|language=en|archive-date=2018-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007183554/https://www.dailystar.co.uk/movies/718111/fantastic-beats-crimes-grindelwald-nicholas-flamel-dumbledore-newt-scamander-harry-potter|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

